# CitedBy.ai — Instructions Projet

> **Derniere mise a jour** : 2026-02-21 — Migration Next.js App Router terminee

## Architecture

- **Next.js App Router** — Single frontend framework (Vite SPA eliminated)
- **43 pages** in `views/` (original components) wrapped by `app/(app)/*/page.tsx`
- **17 AI API routes** in `app/api/ai/` (server-side Gemini calls)
- **20+ services** in `services/` (15 root + 3 subdirectories)
- **15 composants** in `components/`
- **i18n** in `i18n/` (FR/EN/ES) — custom React Context
- **Data layer** : localStorage (via `services/database.ts`)
- Design : dark theme Tailwind, accents purple/violet

## Commandes

- `npm run dev` → Next.js dev server (port 3000)
- `npm run build` → Production build
- `npm start` → Start production server
- `npm run lint` → ESLint
- `npm test` → Vitest

## Stack technique

- **Frontend** : Next.js 14 App Router, React 18, Tailwind CSS, Lucide Icons
- **AI** : Google Gemini (@google/genai) via server-side API routes, fallback simulation
- **Auth** : Supabase (Auth) + localStorage mock login
- **Paiement** : Stripe (interface unifiee StripeCheckout)
- **i18n** : Custom React Context (FR/EN/ES)
- **Validation** : Zod + React Hook Form
- **Charts** : Recharts
- **PDF** : jsPDF

