## Regles importantes

- Gemini API calls go through server-side API routes (`app/api/ai/`)
- Pages in `views/` receive props from `useAppContext()` via page wrappers
- NE PAS modifier services/analyzer.ts, services/criteria.ts, services/generator.ts
- AI generation uses GoogleGenAI with fallback simulation if API key absent
- Design: dark theme bg-[#0F172A], border-white/5, rounded-2xl
- Palette accents: gradient purple-500 → violet-600, text-purple-400
- AI Overviews uses rose #f43f5e

## Key Patterns

### Adding a new page
1. Create view component in `views/NewPage.tsx`
2. Add route mapping in `lib/route-map.ts`
3. Create `app/(app)/section/new-page/page.tsx` wrapper using `useAppContext()`
4. Add to sidebar in `components/layout/AppSidebar.tsx`

### Adding a new AI service
1. Create service in `services/new-service.ts`
2. Create API route in `app/api/ai/new-service/route.ts`
3. Add client wrapper in `lib/api-client.ts`
